<li><i>Burl Ives Folio of Australian Songs</i>, collected and arranged by Percy Jones, 1954.</li>
<li><i>Song in America: Our Musical Heritage</i>, co-authored with Albert Hague. New York: Duell, Sloan and Pearce, n.d.</li>
<li><i>Tales of America</i>. Cleveland: World Publishing, 1954</li>
