<li><i>Spoken Arts Treasury of American Ballads and Folk Songs</i>, co-authored with Arthur Klein and Helen Ives, n.d.</li>
<li><i>Easy Guitar Method</i>. Dayton, Ohio&#160;: Heritage Music Press, 1975</li>
